text: Temple of Low Men is the second studio album by rock band Crowded House and was released on 5 July 1988 through Capitol Records. It went to number 1 in Australia, number 2 in New Zealand, number 10 in Canada, number 20 in the Netherlands, number 40 in the United States and number 99 in the United Kingdom. == Track listing == Category:1988 albums Category:Crowded House
title: Temple of Low Men
